Homey

Homey is the second studio album by the American math rock band Chon. It was released on June 16, 2017, through Sumerian Records. It was the band's first release not to feature bassist Drew Pelisek.

Grow

Grow is the debut studio album by American progressive rock band Chon. It was released on March 23, 2015, through Sumerian Records. It was the band's last release to feature bassist Drew Pelisek.

Newborn Sun

Newborn Sun is another one of Chons few albums release by the American progressive rock band Chon. It was released on June 11, 2013 is another one of the albums to feature bass player Drew Pelisek and master by Daniel Castelman.{" "}

Woohoo!

Woohoo! is another debut studio album by American progressive rock band Chon. It was released on March 23, 2015, through Sumerian Records. It was the band's last release to feature bassist Drew Pelisek.
